metadata.name: Recovery
metadata.description:
This is funny somehow, I created this piece in the first months when I met my soulmate and I was very happy.
Now I minted this piece when I am a lone soul, heartbroken. I have to recover from recovery, kind of. 

This is the first time I speak loud about my feelings. Feels weird.
